3.5  Presentation Format
Duration: 10 minutes presentation + 5 minutes Q&A.
Slides: maximum 10 slides (title, problem, approach, findings, recommendations, and call to action).
Format: PowerPoint or PDF presented over screen share during the Week 10 session.
All team members must contribute to the presentation — facilitators will note if only one person speaks.

