3.7  Recognition
All completed Capstone projects receive a Certificate of Completion.
The top three projects are publicly recognised at the Week 10 closing ceremony.
Outstanding projects may be shared on the SLEDGE LinkedIn page and recommended to partner organisations.
Participants who lead a top-three project are given priority consideration for SLEDGE Plus and internship linkages.
